(22865, 'After Koutarou Satomi\'s father is suddenly relocated for his job, the first-year high school student is faced with finding a cheap place to live by himself. Naturally, he jumps at the chance to move into Corona House\'s Room 106 for a mere five thousand yen a month. But while everything goes well at first, Koutarou soon gets a lot more than he bargained for after stumbling upon a mysterious cave while working his part-time job. The following night, Koutarou is visited by various seemingly mythical figures, all of whom claim ownership of the poor student\'s apartment. Among the invaders are Sanae Higashihongan, a ghost supposedly haunting the room, magical girl Yurika, alien princess Theiamillis Gre Fortorthe, and Kiriha Kurano, a direct descendant of the Earth People. But more importantly, each of these four girls needs Koutarou\'s apartment for her own reasons and won’t back down without a fight! Rokujouma no Shinryakusha!? is a comedic battle royale over a six-tatami mat apartment involving supernatural beings, romantic high school hijinks, and a deceptively cordial landlady. [Written by MAL Rewrite]', '23 min per ep', 0, 12, 'Finished Airing', '2014-07-12', '2014-09-27', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/2/62655.jpg', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 'TV', 'Rokujouma no Shinryakusha!?', '六畳間の侵略者！？', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/8ZKg5HOSuF4?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1', 300),
