(31056, 'Specials bundled with limited edition Blu-ray/DVD volumes of the Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya 2wei Herz!.', '6 min per ep', 0, 5, 'Finished Airing', '2015-09-25', '2016-01-29', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/7/81262.jpg', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 'Special', 'Fate/kaleid liner Prisma☆Illya 2wei Herz! Specials', 'Fate/kaleid liner プリズマ☆イリヤ ツヴァイ ヘルツ！ショートアニメ', 'NULL', 300),
(31080, 'Tennomifune Academy is an elite institution for the best and the brightest, with the exception of Class 1-7, the so-called \"Happiness Class.\" Each member of the classroom copes with personal misfortunes, and the special class is geared to help them move past their issues and find true happiness. After being accepted into the academy, An Hanakoizumi, Ruri Hibarigaoka, and Botan Kumegawa find themselves placed into the Happiness Class, plagued by dreadful luck, love problems, and bad health respectively. Alongside their classmates, they do their best to overcome the difficulties they are faced with in pursuit of a life filled with joy. [Written by MAL Rewrite]', '23 min per ep', 0, 12, 'Finished Airing', '2016-04-07', '2016-06-23', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/9/78701.jpg', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 'TV', 'Anne Happy♪', 'あんハピ♪', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/zoRwNAyEHBg?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1', 300),
