(35078, 'The \"Colors\" are three cute little girls who hang out together and protect the peace of their city. They have lots of fun together, doing stuff like playing games, solving puzzles, and going to the zoo. This anime follows their largely happy daily life. (Source: MangaHelpers, edited)', '23 min per ep', 0, 12, 'Finished Airing', '2018-01-07', '2018-03-25', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/5/89984.jpg', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 'TV', 'Mitsuboshi Colors', '三ツ星カラーズ', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lqDhsdx_oqs?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1', 300),
(35082, 'Following their success in the qualifying round for the Kansai regional competition, the members of the Kitauji High School concert band set their sights on the next upcoming performance. Utilizing their summer break to the utmost, the band participates in a camp where they are instructed by their band advisor Noboru Taki and his friends who make their living as professional musicians. Kumiko Oumae and her friends remain determined to attain gold at the Kansai competition, but trouble arises when a student who once quit the band shows interest in rejoining and sparks unpleasant memories for the second-year members. Kumiko also learns about her teacher\'s surprising past and the motivation behind his desire to lead the band to victory. Reaching nationals will require hard work, and the adamant conviction in each student\'s commitment to the band will be put to the test. [Written by MAL Rewrite]', '1 hr 55 min', 0, 1, 'Finished Airing', '2017-09-30', '0000-00-00', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/5/88024.jpg', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 'Movie', 'Hibike! Euphonium Movie 2: Todoketai Melody', '劇場版 響け！ユーフォニアム～届けたいメロディ～', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/qnOa2TFXWRY?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=1', 2),
